Second Department,

April, 1953.

(April 2,1953.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Fred Carchietta et al., Relators, against Warden of the Raymond Street Jail, Borough of Brooklyn, et al., Respondents.

Writ dismissed and relators remanded to the custody of the Warden of the Raymond Street Jail, Brooklyn, Few York. Present — Carswell, Acting, P. J., Adel, MacCrate, Schmidt and Beldoek, J.J.
